The paper discusses the challenges and design considerations for implementing a 5G network architecture, which involves aspects of networking, information theory, augmented reality, systems, and multimedia. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.AR (Augmented Reality), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
